caption: b'#givingtuesday is about coming together for a worldwide celebration of generosity. Our teams in Krakow and Wuppertal are granting wishes and purchasing gifts this holiday season for hundreds of local families in need. And our team in Mexico raised money to benefit the Association for Youth and Children with Special Needs through United Way Chihuahua. :wrapped_gift: \n\nThese are just a few examples of how our teams are working to give back to the communities where we work and live. #ItsOurMove #givingback'

b'Meet Nicole, she started at Aptiv more than 20 years ago as a college intern and is now a senior advanced development engineer. At the beginning of her career, Nicole set out to join the ranks of Aptiv\xe2\x80\x99s top innovators in the Innovation Hall of Fame. Last year, she became the first female engineer from North America to reach this milestone. As a mother of two young girls, she says this is her proudest accomplishment. Here\xe2\x80\x99s her advice for up-and-coming innovators:'

b"Good food, time with family, and a bit of a mess in the kitchen is sometimes what we need to feel connected during this time of distancing.
